# name	host	port	role	state	note
boss	local	-	boss	local	Owns priority stack, frontier/current-target lock, policy visibility, dispatch, and no-submit gate.
auditor	local	-	auditor	local	Bluesky/Redsky/RCI/PUA/PIP audit lane; implements process fixes and demands evidence.
pua-pip	local	-	pua-pip	local	Repeated-failure discipline, assumption inversion, and sharper bounded checks.
researcher	local	-	researcher	local	Theory and paper-to-source construction lane; source-bound packets only.
source-proof	local	-	source-proof	local	Source novelty, support invariants, counterexamples, and closed-ledger screens.
validator	local	-	validator	local	Trusted local validation lane for gate-pass candidates only.
pods-manager	local	-	provider-manager	local	Provider inventory, canaries, spend visibility, worker registry, cleanup plans.
wallbreaker-lead	local	-	wallbreaker	local	Lead integrator: converts specialist output into one route_attempt, worker_attempt, or hard_nack.
wallbreaker-shadow	local	-	wallbreaker	local	Adversarial integrator: falsifies the lead attempt or proposes one materially different alternate.
claude-waffle-lab	local	-	claude-deep-engineer	local	Long-context engineer 1/2, integration and executable packet production.
claude-laser-spatula	local	-	claude-deep-engineer	local	Long-context engineer 2/2, adversarial alternate and falsifier.
claude-research-sommelier	local	-	claude-deep-researcher	local	Long-context researcher, stepwise digestion with audit between batches.
